Ability.Name: Tactical Missile
Ability.Description: Fires missiles that hits all hostiles 4m around the enemy target dealing <<1>> weapon damage to up to 5 targets.

Ability.Name: Calculated Precision
Ability.Description: Fires a precision shot to a target with less than 30% health, dealing <<1>> weapon damage.

Ability.Name: Electro Dart
Ability.Description: Fires an electro dart stunning the target for 5 seconds.

Ability.Name: Blast
Ability.Description: A powerful shot dealt to a single target, dealing <<1>> weapon damage.

Ability.Name: Flame Burst
Ability.Description: Burns the target by dealing <<1>> weapon damage over a 10 second duration and causing the target to become sundered. Sundered targets have their armor reduced by 20% for 45 seconds.

Ability.Name: Kolto Area Scan
Ability.Description: Bursts an area 8m wide with a soothing, lingering Kolto cloud. Heals for <<1>> health over 6 seconds.

Ability.Name: Kolto Shot
Ability.Description: Heals a friendly target for <<1>>.

Ability.Name: Quick Kolto Burst
Ability.Description: Executes a quick Kolto scan on the target, healing for <<1>>.

Ability.Name: Kolto Scan Process
Ability.Description: Slowly heals the target for <<1>> over 9 seconds and cleanses physical and mental effects each time it heals the target.

Ability.Name: Electro-Stasis
Ability.Description: Binds the target in a stasis field for up to 10 seconds. Damage to the target causes this effect to end prematurely. Targets may only be affected by Electro-Stasis once every 30 seconds. Target must not be suffering from periodic damage and have greater than 90% max health.

Ability.Name: Preventative Protocol
Ability.Description: Places a Kolto-powered shield around the target, preventing a moderate amount of damage for up to 20 seconds.

Ability.Name: Electronics Overload
Ability.Description: Activates an explosive that deals <<1>> kinetic damage to up to 5 enemies 5m around the user. Generates a moderate amount of threat and reduces incoming damage by 50% for 10 seconds. Does not hit sleeping, lifted, or incapacitated enemies.

Ability.Name: Multi-Grapple
Ability.Description: Fires a multi-grapple line that fires in a wide cone in front of the companion and pulls the closest three targets and generates a high amount of threat. Only affects targets that are in combat and are not in cover or have Boss Immunity.

Ability.Name: Provoking Flare
Ability.Description: Fires a flare taunting attacking enemies forcing them to attack your companion and generates a moderate amount of threat.

Ability.Name: Powered Shot
Ability.Description: Blasts the target, dealing <<1>> weapon damage, heals for 25% of damage dealt and generates a moderate amount of threat.

Ability.Name: Reinforcing Taunt
Ability.Description: Taunts the target, forcing it to attack the companion for 6 seconds. Also reinforces the companion by placing an absorb shield that absorbs a moderate amount of damage.

Ability.Name: Portable Carbonite Turret
Ability.Description: Deploys a Portable Sentry Turret at your location to aid in combat. The Turret lasts 30 seconds and generates a high amount of threat with its attacks.

Ability.Name: Thermal Grenade
Ability.Description: Throws a grenade, dealing elemental damage over 10 seconds to up to 8 enemies within 8 meters of the targeted area. Additionally, standard and weak enemies are stunned by the flames.

Ability.Name: Portable Missile Turret
Ability.Description: Deploys a Portable Missile Turret at your location to aid in combat. The Turret lasts 30 seconds and deals a high amount of damage with it's attacks.

Ability.Name: Anti-Personnel Rocket
Ability.Description: Fires an Anti-Personnel Rocket, which damages all hostiles within the radius of the explosion.

Ability.Name: Raise/Lower Shield
Ability.Description: Raising your shield blocks ability use and slows movement speed, but lets you block and redirect attacks in your forward arc.

Ability.Name: Portable Sentry Turret
Ability.Description: Deploys a Portable Sentry Turret at your location to aid in combat. The Turret lasts 30 seconds and generates a high amount of threat with its attacks.

Ability.Name: Thermal Grenade
Ability.Description: Throws a grenade, dealing <<1>> elemental damage over 9 seconds to up to 8 enemies within 8 meters of the targeted area. Additionally, standard and weak enemies are stunned by the flames.

Ability.Name: Hilt Strike
Ability.Description: Hilt strike that stuns the target briefly. Will not stun if used by Standard/Weak mobs.

Ability.Name: Leap
Ability.Description: Leaps to the target, immobilizing it for 1.5 seconds and dealing low damage.

Ability.Name: Charging In
Ability.Description: Charge to a distant target, immobilizing it for 2 seconds.

Ability.Name: Rifle Blast
Ability.Description: A series of ranged shots for an NPC

Ability.Name: Extreme Prejudice
Ability.Description: Fires a continuous stream of bolts that deal heavy damage for up to 4 seconds.

Ability.Name: Rail Blast
Ability.Description: Blasts a target for <<1>> energy damage.

Ability.Name: Assassinate
Ability.Description: HK-55 takes careful aim at a target strong, standard, or weak enemy. Deals excessive damage. Not usable in combat.

Ability.Name: Execute
Ability.Description: Deals <<1>> weapon damage to a target below 30% health.

Ability.Name: Weapons Check
Ability.Description: Regenerates health while channeling. Not usable in combat.

Ability.Name: Electro Dart
Ability.Description: Fires an electro dart stunning the target for 5 seconds.

Ability.Name: Blindside
Ability.Description: HK-51 takes advantage of a distracted target, firing a well placed decisive shot for <<1>> weapon damage. Can only be used on stunned targets.

Ability.Name: Force Leap
Ability.Description: Leaps to the target, immobilizing it for 1.5 seconds and dealing low damage.

Ability.Name: Powerful Critical Surge
Ability.Description: Healing an ally or performing a damaging attack on an enemy both have a 30% chance to grant 413 Power and Critical Rating for 6 seconds. This effect can only occur once every 20 seconds.

Ability.Name: Shield Boost
Ability.Description: Incoming attacks have a 30% chance to increase Shield Rating and Absorb Rating by 413 for 6 seconds. This effect can only occur once every 20 seconds.

Ability.Name: Shade Stalker Runt
Ability.Description: Summons a Shade Stalker Runt which will follow and passively observe you on your adventures.

Ability.Name: Model Eternal Flagship
Ability.Description: Summons a Model Eternal Flagship which will follow and passively observe you on your adventures.

Ability.Name: Zakuul Miniprobe
Ability.Description: Summons a small probe droid which will follow and passively observe you on your adventures.

Ability.Name: Activating Requisition...
Ability.Description: Activates your droid operator requisition.

Ability.Name: Opening Hypercrate
Ability.Description: Right-click to open this Hypercrate.

Ability.Name: Surge
Ability.Description: Strikes all nearby targets with the lightsaber, throwing them away from the caster and stunning them briefly.

Ability.Name: Czerka Ranger
Ability.Description:
Activates the Czerka Ranger, increasing movement speed and offering excellent protection against being knocked off. Movement speed increases based on the rank of your Speeder Piloting skill.
Speeder Piloting Rank 1: 90% Speeder Piloting Rank 2: 100% Speeder Piloting Rank 3: 110%
